title: Swim & Splash Kids' Swimming Ring, 60cm, Sea Life Design, Ages 3+, for Pool Beach Garden
features: AGE APPROPRIATE: Designed for children aged 3 years and above, this swimming ring provides safe water fun for young swimmers
VERSATILE USE: Suitable for multiple environments including pools, beaches, and garden water activities for endless summer entertainment
PERFECT SIZE: Measures 60 centimetres in diameter, offering ideal support and stability for children while swimming or playing
PLAYFUL DESIGN: Features charming sea life illustrations including colourful fish, octopus, and coral patterns that appeal to children
DURABLE CONSTRUCTION: Made from sturdy inflatable material that's easy to inflate and deflate for convenient storage and transport
description: Product Description Make a splash this summer with this delightful 60cm swimming ring featuring an enchanting sea life design. Perfect for children aged 3 and above, this vibrant inflatable ring brings underwater adventures to life with its playful marine creatures, including charming octopi and friendly fish, set against a bright blue and yellow background with decorative coral elements. The 60-centimetre size provides excellent buoyancy and stability for young swimmers, making it ideal for use in pools, at the beach, or in the garden paddling pool. The ring's durable construction ensures it can withstand regular use, while its colourful design makes it easy to spot in the water. This Swim & Splash swimming ring combines safety and fun, helping little ones build water confidence while enjoying their aquatic playtime. The convenient size makes it easy to pack for holidays or store when not in use. Remember to always supervise children during water activities and ensure proper inflation before use. Safety Warning Warning: Only to be used in water in which the child is within it's depth and under adult supervision. This is not a Life Saving Device
